					<div class="c-head">
						<a href='http://www.facebook.com/doug.foss.14' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Doug Foss</a> <span class="c-permalink"><a href="http://paxlupo.com/2013/04/13/this-is-not-times-square/#comment-114">permalink</a></span>					</div>
					<div class="c-date">
						April 14, 2013 12:28 pm					</div>
										<p>Serving the higher self, the Buddha, means to serve others.</p>
										<div class="reply">
						<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/04/13/this-is-not-times-square/?replytocom=114#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-114", "114", "respond", "771")'>Reply</a>					</div>
									</div><!--end c-body-->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->

			<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 highlander-comment" id="comment-131" >
			<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/dd2f81d5fd9b792cc4c44fb1fbab808a?s=60&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-60' height='60' width='60' /></div>
				<div class="c-body">
					<div class="c-head">
						Debra <span class="c-permalink"><a href="http://paxlupo.com/2013/04/13/this-is-not-times-square/#comment-131">permalink</a></span>					</div>
					<div class="c-date">
						June 10, 2013 3:56 am					</div>
										<p>Well, Stephen, it looks like we are seeing the same world these days..<br />
Our local shopping center&#8217;s lunchtime eateries are hard, white, metal, or plastic. (The&#8230; ARchiTectic probably believed in what he was doing, but the animal in me either snarls or weeps facing so much disembodied, senseless waste.)<br />
There isn&#8217;t a curve, or a hint of the color green anywhere in sight.<br />
I stay away from the place as much as possible, and actively flee the encroaching artificial world, something which is still possible for me to do.<br />
My resistance is quiet, private, somewhat, but not totally, methodic.<br />
&#8220;We&#8221; are tired of having the imperative of service thrown in our faces, from the Buddha, from Jesus, or from our government. (Remember that the etymology of &#8220;service&#8221; includes the word &#8220;servus&#8221; which was associated with slavery in Antiquity. Very important to remember this.)<br />
This is understandable, I believe, although not inclined to make our lives in this world more comfortable, certainly.<br />
See you around, huh ? <span class='wp-smiley emoji emoji-wink' title=';-)'>;-)</span></p>
										<div class="reply">
						<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/04/13/this-is-not-times-square/?replytocom=131#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-131", "131", "respond", "771")'>Reply</a>					</div>
									</div><!--end c-body-->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->

